Achievements.Name: The Mobile Escapist
Achievements.Description: Escape from all 3 of the base game transport prisons.

Achievements.Name: Good Intentions
Achievements.Description: Go 3 consecutive days without raising your Guard Heat above 0 in a single session.

Achievements.Name: Crook Of All Trades
Achievements.Description: Complete the quota once for each of the jobs over multiple prisons/sessions.

Achievements.Name: Man's Best Friend
Achievements.Description: Gain a high enough opinion from a dog.

Achievements.Name: Pour Us A Brew Will Yer, Love?
Achievements.Description: Make a cup of tea and gift it to another inmate or guard.

Achievements.Name: Dr. Love
Achievements.Description: Get whisked away by a hunky medic.

Achievements.Name: I've Got A Cunning Plan
Achievements.Description: Perform 7 unique escapes across the Classic prisons.

Achievements.Name: I'm The Daddy
Achievements.Description: Knock out every inmate at least once in a single prison.

Achievements.Name: Man's Worst Friend
Achievements.Description: Get mauled by a guard dog.

Achievements.Name: Music Maestro
Achievements.Description: Play on the instruments for 1 hour of in-game time.

Achievements.Name: Are You Lonesome Tonight?
Achievements.Description: Spend 3 days total time in solitary over multiple prisons/sessions.

Achievements.Name: The Cake Is A Lie?
Achievements.Description: Attack a guard with a cake.

Achievements.Name: I Am Your Father...
Achievements.Description: Fight another player in the U.S.S Anomaly, when you are both armed with energy swords.

Achievements.Name: Soap On A Rope
Achievements.Description: Spend 3 days total time in the showers over multiple prisons/sessions.

Achievements.Name: Call Of Snooty
Achievements.Description: Escape H.M.P. Offshore on Snooty the Dolphin.

Achievements.Name: The Naked Chef
Achievements.Description: Complete a quota of the Kitchen job whilst being naked.
